{"image_id": "KEY_2015_page_163", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Most extensions of credit are subject to loan grading or scoring. Loan grades are assigned at the time of", "bbox": [162.5, 159.1, 1026.8, 179.9]}, {"text": "origination, verified by credit risk management, and periodically re-evaluated thereafter. This risk rating", "bbox": [162.5, 184.1, 1034.0, 204.9]}, {"text": "methodology blends our judgment with quantitative modeling. Commercial loans generally are assigned two", "bbox": [162.5, 209.1, 1069.7, 229.9]}, {"text": "internal risk ratings. The first rating reflects the probability that the borrower will default on an obligation; the", "bbox": [162.5, 234.1, 1082.3, 254.9]}, {"text": "second rating reflects expected recovery rates on the credit facility. Default probability is determined based on,", "bbox": [162.5, 259.1, 1089.7, 279.9]}, {"text": "among other factors, the financial strength of the borrower, an assessment of the borrower’s management, the", "bbox": [162.5, 284.1, 1077.2, 304.9]}, {"text": "borrower’s competitive position within its industry sector, and our view of industry risk in the context of the", "bbox": [162.5, 309.1, 1066.9, 329.9]}, {"text": "general economic outlook. Types of exposure, transaction structure, and collateral, including credit risk", "bbox": [162.5, 334.1, 1026.3, 354.9]}, {"text": "mitigants, affect the expected recovery assessment.", "bbox": [162.5, 359.1, 589.7, 379.9]}, {"text": "Credit quality indicators for loans are updated on an ongoing basis. Bond rating classifications are indicative of", "bbox": [162.5, 409.1, 1091.8, 429.9]}, {"text": "the credit quality of our commercial loan portfolios and are determined by converting our internally assigned risk", "bbox": [162.5, 434.1, 1108.8, 454.9]}, {"text": "rating grades to bond rating categories. Payment activity and the regulatory classifications of pass and", "bbox": [162.5, 459.1, 1014.3, 479.9]}, {"text": "substandard are indicators of the credit quality of our consumer loan portfolios.", "bbox": [162.5, 484.1, 824.5, 504.9]}, {"text": "Credit quality indicators for our commercial and consumer loan portfolios, excluding $11 million and $13", "bbox": [162.5, 534.1, 1047.8, 554.9]}, {"text": "million of PCI loans at December 31, 2015, and December 31, 2014, respectively, based on bond rating,", "bbox": [162.5, 559.1, 1032.6, 579.9]}, {"text": "regulatory classification, and payment activity as of December 31, 2015, and December 31, 2014, are as follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 584.1, 1105.3, 604.9]}, {"text": "Commercial Credit Exposure", "bbox": [162.5, 633.9, 425.4, 654.7]}, {"text": "Credit Risk Profile by Creditworthiness Category (a)", "bbox": [162.5, 658.9, 624.7, 679.7]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [162.5, 707.0, 235.3, 719.5]}, {"text": "in millions", "bbox": [162.5, 723.6, 215.6, 736.1]}, {"text": "Commercial, financial and", "bbox": [311.4, 746.6, 453.2, 759.1]}, {"text": "agricultural", "bbox": [350.4, 763.2, 414.3, 775.7]}, {"text": "RE — Commercial", "bbox": [497.9, 763.2, 600.0, 775.7]}, {"text": "RE — Construction", "bbox": [656.1, 763.2, 762.4, 775.7]}, {"text": "Commercial Lease", "bbox": [820.0, 763.2, 919.5, 775.7]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [1022.2, 763.2, 1050.7, 775.7]}, {"text": "RATING (b), (c)", "bbox": [162.5, 788.2, 237.8, 800.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [346.9, 788.2, 371.9, 800.7]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [433.3, 788.2, 458.3, 800.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [513.5, 788.2, 538.5, 800.7]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [593.8, 788.2, 618.8, 800.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [674.0, 788.2, 699.0, 800.7]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [754.2, 788.2, 779.2, 800.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [834.4, 788.2, 859.4, 800.7]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [914.6, 788.2, 939.6, 800.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [1001.0, 788.2, 1026.0, 800.7]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [1087.5, 788.2, 1112.5, 800.7]}, {"text": "AAA — AA", "bbox": [162.5, 811.3, 226.5, 823.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [306.2, 